108
00:13:00,837 --> 00:13:02,071
What did he look like?

109
00:13:02,072 --> 00:13:03,732
Do you remember?

110
00:13:03,732 --> 00:13:05,275
Of course.

111
00:13:05,275 --> 00:13:07,368
He was…

112
00:13:07,368 --> 00:13:09,954
About 5'7".

113
00:13:09,955 --> 00:13:12,182
Just a regular-looking dude.

114
00:13:12,182 --> 00:13:16,369
In his early thirties, max.

115
00:13:16,369 --> 00:13:19,297
He was wearing a black T-shirt with white stains

116
00:13:19,298 --> 00:13:23,559
and a pair of khaki hiking pants.

117
00:13:23,559 --> 00:13:25,895
We just need to find him.

118
00:13:25,895 --> 00:13:27,865
