130
00:14:05,001 --> 00:14:07,987
That yogurt drink…

131
00:14:07,987 --> 00:14:11,399
Where and how did you find it?

132
00:14:26,131 --> 00:14:29,192
Did you see anyone else there?

133
00:14:29,192 --> 00:14:31,803
If there was, I wouldn't be in this state right now.

134
00:14:31,803 --> 00:14:33,314
There was no one to help me,

135
00:14:33,314 --> 00:14:37,131
