137
00:14:40,963 --> 00:14:44,717
I guess the story was true.

138
00:14:45,484 --> 00:14:47,877
About the ghost, you know.

139
00:14:47,877 --> 00:14:49,113
The ghost?

140
00:14:49,113 --> 00:14:51,723
There's a male ghost on the mountain these days.

141
00:14:51,724 --> 00:14:55,226
And the rumor is that you die soon after seeing him.

142
00:14:55,227 --> 00:14:57,395
I didn't believe it at first.

143
00:14:57,396 --> 00:15:02,150
But I saw that ghost with my own eyes a few days ago.

144
00:15:02,151 --> 00:15:03,776
Yes, coming!

145
00:15:03,777 --> 00:15:07,580
I hid because I thought he was a ranger,

146
00:15:09,116 --> 00:15:10,908
but he looked weird.

147
00:15:10,909 --> 00:15:13,520
He was covered in blood.

148
00:15:14,221 --> 00:15:16,164
A ranger?

149
00:15:17,191 --> 00:15:20,476
That logo on your uniform.

150
00:15:20,476 --> 00:15:23,922
It was on the back of his jumper.

151
00:15:23,923 --> 00:15:28,176
It was white and this long

152
00:15:28,177 --> 00:15:31,138
with that logo on the back.

153
00:15:31,138 --> 00:15:33,781
Do you mean a snowsuit?

154
00:15:33,781 --> 00:15:36,576
I don't know what that is.

155
00:15:42,274 --> 00:15:45,268
Do you mean this jumper?

156
00:15:45,861 --> 00:15:47,921
It's him.

157
00:15:49,031 --> 00:15:50,156
What do you mean?

158
00:15:50,157 --> 00:15:51,508
It's that man.

159
00:15:51,508 --> 00:15:54,536
The ghost I was talking about.

160
00:15:54,536 --> 00:15:56,305
I'm sure of it.

161
00:15:56,305 --> 00:15:57,872
Who is he?

162
00:15:57,873 --> 00:15:59,349
Is he really a ranger?

163
00:15:59,349 --> 00:16:03,127
Why's he covered in blood?

164
00:16:03,712 --> 00:16:06,106
Just because you don't understand them, it doesn't mean they're lies.

165
00:16:06,106 --> 00:16:08,124
It gave me a gift. To save people.

166
00:16:08,124 --> 00:16:09,234
I saw it.

167
00:16:09,234 --> 00:16:10,486
Where the lost hikers are…

168
00:16:10,486 --> 00:16:12,395
Kang Hyun Jo.

169
00:16:14,573 --> 00:16:16,274
Hello?

170
00:16:17,426 --> 00:16:20,661
Yi Kang! It's been so long.

171
00:16:20,661 --> 00:16:22,772
