172
00:16:22,772 --> 00:16:26,609
Are you keeping up with rehab training?

173
00:16:26,609 --> 00:16:30,346
So how can I help you?

174
00:16:33,775 --> 00:16:35,752
Hyun Jo…

175
00:16:36,486 --> 00:16:38,438
How is he doing?

176
00:16:43,018 --> 00:16:45,895
He's fine.

177
00:16:45,895 --> 00:16:47,939
Did he…

178
00:16:49,174 --> 00:16:53,128
