179
00:16:53,128 --> 00:16:56,222
No, nothing like that has happened.

180
00:16:56,222 --> 00:17:00,018
But he's hanging in there.

181
00:17:02,604 --> 00:17:04,956
Okay, thank you.

182
00:17:13,714 --> 00:17:15,942
Yi Kang?

183
00:17:15,942 --> 00:17:18,987
I heard you came back… I guess it's true.

184
00:17:18,987 --> 00:17:21,205
I was very worried about you.

185
00:17:21,206 --> 00:17:23,875
I'm glad you look healthy.

186
00:17:26,186 --> 00:17:29,922
Do you need a ride to the ranger station?

187
00:17:29,922 --> 00:17:32,408
No, it's all right.

188
00:17:32,408 --> 00:17:34,361
Okay, then…

189
00:17:35,220 --> 00:17:37,422
You know…

190
00:17:38,682 --> 00:17:40,950
What you said back then.

191
00:17:42,494 --> 00:17:46,122
That anything's possible on the mountain.

192
00:17:46,122 --> 00:17:47,607
Yes.

193
00:17:52,112 --> 00:17:54,405
Could there really be a ghost on the mountain?

194
00:17:54,406 --> 00:17:58,534
Could all the folk tales told about the mountains be false?

195
00:17:58,535 --> 00:18:01,496
You know they call Jirisan the mountain of patience.

196
00:18:01,497 --> 00:18:03,998
There are more people who climb with a story or two

197
00:18:03,999 --> 00:18:06,584
