198
00:18:06,585 --> 00:18:09,446
Those people have sorrow and regret.

199
00:18:10,047 --> 00:18:13,091
And ghosts are all about sorrow and regret.

200
00:18:13,091 --> 00:18:16,260
For those with a strong desire,

201
00:18:16,261 --> 00:18:19,531
